[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Evaluating native testing constraints**\n\nI'm thinking the native test likely runs the test method within a native executable. However, using a scanner with the JUnit launcher over classpath roots might not work under native conditions unless the class files are available. But it seems like there’s a limitation on open-ended dynamic class loading since it only scans classes recognized at build time. I wonder if I could encounter an UnsupportedFeatureError, but maybe that's just a regular concern.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0075baf0ccae12af016a28a8f4a158819591ab52209a1cf5a0\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqKKkZv4pT88ZKa2ikzW4MdhM2kXY-ij4HGssyN3xzbcEZ_LjfrBtJqunsjm5OtwS7ZLvEsSTqHYuW_92szyvrJFP68w-38xKBh1timertE5H0cQB5UauFKgqNL67TEXhwEKOglCe-BiidkHklTq1U9PgP9TTGkPe2dTudr3uZwotHpWF_6d7ItHWBF5v87u8EZGiu9Asy6KyA1MPR7z6Eu2loGQqUIcAgQ1LDGsp0F07MGdD9KupAFqGt5vk-GKs3RiAFVEEZ0DGpI9xZyMvh68sQ_Rr5tNRl_RWiOY2D1WTOkhktmPng1BZNtUxgs682R5JCWVZo-r-EbQJRUs-MKvqpe5154dOeypRkT-XL0-pBjSv-SWThUj719snTgpWQ_lPM0ugMsNZoDLv1KU4FRFpkpuVuGkj0eRmwirtNuptkY3EPz2Oz2zavyb4wbC6hPk5Zwmztm6anatqlUqa7Wf04BVfbrHe31sjlsxaGFoKdq-wCNU_5AP_Pb3ZFH2jTzhcFF983CbUncAp2GpJ-6Vp_KRdIYVA2ewZdAyCvGmky9_U5Wd52PREH9_syKxU-MKa2IzXgRWfqpJXavbXgI_-ps-wE8Qw6QcJEQi-JhAgc_pasdeng9i0jUkZUci27ERs7W2clZ2KuXlrVgtRaM_11duLgjMxPblxl5qjwOCZ9IgH5nVgxmX83s3B9sEhAoLVrHBhkSixE2ZTMF00bam2jUVhcmSmhZdveXclBMXGPYpRupf_J0cQ07QfFUj4X9nQkvEjRu5U8Z-UvxWMlgGRZ4qeA8IoGz1ENm4mPVIOXCMiwhAwLYx56CRApWr_CzJbYOlUmL5SCYCxpAabcZ6vBDD4Tnd1oEuPNq7y5xFo8fmZ75skNHxTkF7qBrxzQ7YIoxe5-Unv71vguF-cyZ2Bo9WcGyNUk8efAeOeFlt6GeXocrAQCt0GJpHDkT8DGvixVeQ4GD4e9QiY8T1WhO96eP8BaeD93T0aeLOsjfTti1vpJ-k-1dUXsDkYOHq_f4UtdfAMnqxZpjxPo-tA5CTKmMa1lJFU5yMLGShxxFFXdyzu9ZaTMxX_31b07svnrAB2CJuGddyyxaEPYuoatZcu4DNX7Mwl3lb5i65vmuboULWIgtiRsAMj67H0fcr-hFkvA9l9bLr6mY4Iu7NSriEDypf5JkJ3BFpLOYiEkx09bm4erOhM8eGD5ZeFQX7AtaNKlgS7CJ